      serialVersionUID:
      1L

      • Serialized Fields

        • inputs

          Deque<E> inputs
          Record all the inputs until commit.

        • streamingCheckpointEnabled

          boolean streamingCheckpointEnabled
          If checkpoint is enabled we should do nothing in CommitterOperator.endInput. Remaining data will be committed in CommitterOperator.notifyCheckpointComplete(long). If checkpoint is not enabled we need to commit remaining data in CommitterOperator.endInput.

        • initialCommitUser

          String initialCommitUser
          This commitUser is valid only for new jobs. After the job starts, this commitUser will be recorded into the states of write and commit operators. When the job restarts, commitUser will be recovered from states and this value is ignored.

        • committablesPerCheckpoint

          NavigableMap<K,V> committablesPerCheckpoint
          Group the committable by the checkpoint id.

        • committerFactory

          SerializableFunction<T,R> committerFactory

        • committableStateManager

          CommittableStateManager committableStateManager

        • committer

          Committer committer
          Aggregate committables to global committables and commit the global committables to the external system.

        • endInput

          boolean endInput
